trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] A <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> maintains two UserTrackingLocationCollection objects: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A> specifies parameters used for matching activity status events and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A> specifies parameters used to exclude activity status events from matching.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>mantém dois objetos UserTrackingLocationCollection: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A>Especifica os parâmetros usados para eventos de status de atividade de correspondência e <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A>Especifica os parâmetros usados para excluir eventos de status de atividade de correspondência.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: The default constructor initializes the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection> to an empty list.
trans-unit.target: O construtor padrão inicializa o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection>para uma lista vazia.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection"></xref> class by using a list of user locations.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection"> </xref> classe usando uma lista de locais de usuário.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection> is initialized to contain the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation> objects specified in `locations`.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection>é inicializada para conter o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation>objetos especificados em `locations`.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection>
